\pard\ql\sb200\sa80\f0\fs24\cf0\sl360\slmult1\b 9.1  Skenario Tugas Usability Testing\par
\pard\qj\sb0\sa120\f0\fs24\cf0\sl360\slmult1\b0 Sebelum mengisi kuesioner SUS, seluruh 10 responden diminta menyelesaikan 3 skenario tugas nyata berikut:\par
\pard\sb0\sa80\par
